<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Welcome to Expunge.io for Illinois</h2>
</div> 

    <p>If you were arrested when you were 17 or younger, you probably have a juvenile record - these records do not go away on their own.</p>
    <p>The good news: most juvenile records can be erased through a process called <b>juvenile expungement!</b></p>


<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Juvenile Expungement 1-2-3</h2>
</div> 

<div class="row" id='action-steps'>

	<div class="span4">
		<div class='well'>
			<h4>1. Find out if you're eligible for juvenile expungement</h4>
			<%= link_to('<button id="medium-text">START!</button>'.html_safe, disclaimer_path, :method => "get") %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="span4">
		<div class='well'>
			<h4 >2. Get your arrest information (rap sheet)</h4>
		
		<%= link_to('<button id="medium-text">Find Out How</button>'.html_safe, step2_path, :method => "get") %>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="span4">
		<div class='well'>
			<h4>3. Apply for expungement</h4>
		
			<%= link_to('<button id="medium-text">Get Paperwork</button>'.html_safe, step3_path, :method => "get") %>
		</div>

	</div>
	
</div>


